    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride that\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in solid shape and runs like a dream! It has a few minor signs of love from over the years, but it\u2019s super reliable and totally ready for its next adventure with you. It's been perfect for my daily commutes and weekend getaways, and I know you'll love it too. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
