    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Titan Silver. At its heart is the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. The power is sent to the rear wheels via a 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive valve adjustment. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed control arm bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup provides the communicative feedback these chassis are known for. While the exterior reflects its honest 'good' condition status with minor cosmetic road wear, the drivetrain is robust and ready for the apex.",
